Title: Batch of speckled grey tiles sqm
Description:
Batch of speckled grey tiles.

Dimensions: 100 mm x 100 mm (+/- 1 mm)
Thickness: +/- 7 mm
Quantity: 11 sqm

Good used condition, some of the tiles may have a few chips and scratches. The mortar is completely removed using an acid bath (the tile itself is insensitive to acids). A bit dusty, needs to be cleaned with brush and soap after installation.

Colour may slightly vary from a tile to another.
